config MS5803_05BA
	bool "TE MS5803-05BA pressure and temperature sensor"
	default y
	depends on SENSOR
	depends on SPI
	depends on DT_HAS_ARGISENSE_MS5803_05BA_ENABLED
	help
	  Enable the TE Connectivity MS5803-05BA digital absolute pressure
	  sensor driver. The driver uses the Zephyr Sensor API and supports the
	  SPI wiring used by the ArgiSense methane + pressure board.
